_json.title: How to Get a Trapped Hummingbird Out of The House Safely
_json.gridTitle: How to Get a Trapped Hummingbird Out of The House Safely
_json.description: Inquisitive hummingbirds are likely to investigate any potential food source. And their curiosity can get them in trouble when they get stuck inside not knowing how to get out of there. These birds like to explore different areas of a garden. And any place where there is red, whether natural or artificial, is likely to attract your attention. When this happens, birds can be trapped somewhere that is not safe for them, such as garages, sheds, theaters, and houses. When the bird discovers that...
